This patch is not perfect and has one big challenge. How do we decouple ourselves for KMSSpillKeyProvider to not use the DistributedFileSystem for getting the key provider shown below. What does it take for the RM to provide an independent key provider.

{code}KeyProvider keyProvider = ((DistributedFileSystem)FileSystem.get(getConf())).getKeyProvider();
{code}

I appreciate any and all comments on the same.
